(4, 'Digital Switching Over', 'online-offline-business-transformation', 2, 6, 'online offline business transformation', '&quot;In short, it is possible to describe digital switching over as putting &quot;offline&quot; business processes into  &quot;online&quot;.', '<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Many owners find themselves lost in the middle of the confusion as companies begin the transformation into the first phases of their reopening. You are not alone if this is you.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">It is difficult to keep up with changes in ability, safety laws, and, most importantly, consumer behavior.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">The good news is that you can take a few quick steps to make the change considerably smoother.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Brick and mortar firms are struggling in an effort to change their establishments as a result of the pandemic and social distancing protocols.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Although it can sound daunting, you will better prepare yourself for the future by knowing the current trends.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">The exponential confirmation of digital platforms, as well as the digitization of popular business processes, is undoubtedly the most important change.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">recently, particularly during the pandemic and the changes it brought with, the idea of digitization, or digital transformation, has gained traction.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Although 500 businesses witnessing these changes used to be a chance, the word has spread like wildfire into tiny business circles around the world. Still, with all the limitations involved, there is considerable doubt on how to accomplish this as a small company.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Thankfully, as we enter a modern age of consumerism, it is not only doable but can make the difference between success and failure.</p><h2 style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><strong>meaning of digital switching over</strong></h2><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">\"In short, it is possible to describe digital switching over as putting \"offline\" business processes into&nbsp; \"online\".</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">It is the use of digital technology to support communication, sales, information, data, recruiting, and just about everything else that you can think of. Moreover, it is a natural progression of the business process that can lead to improved efficiency, better business practices, and an improvement in the bottom line if accurately done.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Technology has been a higher engine of communication and customer behavior.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">In terms of managing their own consumption, it has increased the degree of power the customer has, as well as opened the door to an exceptional level of option.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">At the same time, the enhanced exposure helps your client to connect with your company across a number of online platforms, such as your website, social media, reviews, blogs, and online advertising.</p><h2 style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><strong>Digital switching over examples&nbsp;</strong></h2><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Here are the most popular/essential steps you can take:</p><p style=\"margin-left:!important;\">Marketing email versus direct mail and handouts.</p><ul><li>Getting e-sign contracts for clients vs. contracts that are written out.</li><li>Online financial and cash tracked and accounted for vs. a ledger.</li><li>In the local newspaper, web advertising vs. ads.</li><li>Estimates and virtual appointments versus in-person meetings.</li></ul><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">These few changes can make principal differences in the way you stay in touch with your customer stand and modify the perception of your brand.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">It is important to keep up with the ever-changing requirements of our clients in today\'s day and age.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">It can be a lack of willingness to change, as we have seen many times in the past, that makes the difference between opening new locations and closing doors.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">It is important to remember, in addition to the guidelines, that the benefits resulting from this improvement in the protocol are not just external.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">You will save both time and money from the improved organizational structure resulting from the streamlining of your records, correspondence, and financials.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">You would be able to make data-backed choices by keeping track of all that goes in and out of your business (in all senses).</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">This will allow you to recognize channels that drive the most ROI, cut inefficient processes, and drive vital change on a large scale.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">In this era of rapid digital transformation, the role of <a href=\"https://cpapai.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span style=\"color:hsl(210,75%,60%);\"><strong><u>New Jersey Accounting Services</u></strong></span></a> becomes crucial for businesses adapting to new operational models. These services offer expert guidance in managing the financial aspects of digitization, ensuring accurate tracking of transactions, and aiding in strategic decision-making, which is essential for success in the current economic climate.</p>', 'Online offline business transformation', 'Here are the most popular/essential steps you can take:  Marketing email versus direct mail and handouts.  Getting e-sign contracts for clients vs. contracts that are written out. Online financial and cash tracked and accounted for vs. a ledger. In the local newspaper, web advertising vs. ads. Estimates and virtual appointments versus in-person meetings.', 'Online business, Offline business, Transformation', 'index, follow', 'Digital Switching Over', 'article', '1', '{\"alt\":\"online offline business transformation\",\"src\":\"online-offline-business-transformation-Cpapai.com.webp\"}', NULL, '2023-09-12 06:47:27', '2024-01-21 19:04:58'),
(5, 'Second Financial Impact Payments: IRS Report', 'second-economic-impact-payment', 2, 3, 'Second Economic Impact Payment', 'The IRS added information about the second batch of Economic Impact Payments to the Get My Payment site. The technology is currently in high demand due to the massive amount of payments being sent out and people using it.', '<h2 style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Second Financial Impact Payments: IRS Report</h2><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">The IRS added information about the second batch of Economic Impact Payments to the Get My Payment site. The technology is currently in high demand due to the massive amount of payments being sent out and people using it.<br><br>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">While the IRS was able to provide the second wave of Economic Impact Payments at record speed, we recognize that there are a lot of concerns, and we appreciate everyone\'s patience during this time.<br><br>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Here are some frequently asked questions about getting My Payment and the second round of Economic Impact Payments.<br><br>&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Do you have trouble accessing the Get Payment tool?</h2><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Due to the high volume of visitors, some users may see a \"please wait\" or \"error\" message. The notice \"please wait\" is a standard component of the site\'s function. People are encouraged to return at a later time. There is also a daily limit on how many times customers can use Get My Payment. When the maximum number of accesses is reached, Get My Payment will notify users that they must return the next day.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-left:0px;\">have you not received your deposit yet?&nbsp;</h2><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Perhaps. For individuals receiving the second Economic Impact Payment, the IRS updated Get My Payment (GMP) on January 5, 2021. Please keep an eye on any new developments that may have an impact on your payment. If you checked GMP on or after January 5 and found the following:<br><br>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Your money is deposited after GMP reflects a direct deposit date and partial account information.<br><br>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">The GMP indicates when your payment was mailed; however, it could take up to 3–4 weeks for you to receive it. Keep an eye out for a cheque or a debit card in your mail.<br><br>&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Why is it that the IRS refuses to send me a second Economic Impact Payment by mail?<br><br>&nbsp;</h2><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">The IRS is striving to convey the second Economic Impact Payment rapidly, as legally necessary while planning for the 2021 assessment documenting season. Because of the compacted timetable, the IRS can\'t reissue and mail checks if somebody\'s undeliverable sent installment is gotten back to the IRS. They should record their 2020 assessment form electronically to guarantee and get the Recovery Rebate Credit as fast as could be expected.&nbsp;<br><br>&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Would I be able to call the IRS, programming organization, or bank to determine issues with my Economic Impact Payment?&nbsp;<br><br>&nbsp;</h2><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Individuals should visit IRS.gov for the most current data on the second round of Economic Impact Payments as opposed to calling the office, their monetary organizations, or duty programming suppliers. IRS telephone assistors don\'t have extra data past what\'s accessible on IRS.gov.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Amidst these challenging financial times, the expertise of <a href=\"https://cpapai.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span style=\"color:hsl(210,75%,60%);\"><strong><u>New Jersey Financial Planning Firms</u></strong></span></a> becomes invaluable. These firms specialize in guiding individuals and businesses through complex financial landscapes, such as navigating Economic Impact Payments and other pandemic-related financial changes, ensuring thorough planning and effective management of finances.</p>', 'What to know about the Second Stimulus Checks ?', 'The second Economic Impact Payment, also known as stimulus check or stimulus payment, refers to the second round of direct payments provided to eligible individuals and families by the U.S. government in response to the COVID-19 pandemic', 'Stimulus check, Stimulus payment', 'index, follow', 'Second Financial Impact Payments: IRS Report', 'article', '1', '{\"alt\":\"Second Economic Impact Payment-Stimulus check-Stimulus payment\",\"src\":\"Second-Economic-Impact-Payment.webp\"}', NULL, '2023-09-12 08:43:39', '2024-01-21 19:00:32'),
(6, 'Senior Staff Accountant – Clifton, NJ', 'senior-staff-accountant-clifton-nj', 3, 1, 'senior staff accountant job description', 'Prepare and process journal entries for miscellaneous accounts that may include AP, AR, GL, Inventory, investments, intercompany and other financial transactions.', '<h2 style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><strong>Job Description</strong></h2><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Prepare and process journal entries for miscellaneous<br>accounts that may include AP, AR, GL, Inventory, investments, intercompany and other financial<br>transactions. Perform account reconciliations to ensure the accuracy of account balances and proper<br>accounting treatment of transactions. Perform monthly, quarterly and annual closing activities<br>including, reconciliations, adjusting entries. Prepare worksheets, financial statements, and reports to<br>provide management with information for decision making, and to ensure that all reporting<br>requirements are satisfied. Monitor changes in IFRS, local US GAAP and company Accounting<br>Policies as they relate to assigned area of responsibility. Work closely with other branch team to<br>continuously improve efficacy handoffs or transitions of work. Maintain and balance subsidiary<br>accounts by verifying, allocating, posting, reconciling and resolving discrepancies. Prepare combined<br>financial statements including Balance Sheets, Statements of Income, Statement of Changes in<br>Stockholders’ Equity and Statements of Cash Flows. Establish, document, and perform internal control<br>procedures to ensure accurate and timely financial reporting. Resolve complex reconciling issues and<br>discrepancies and make corrective adjustments. Performs monthly reconciliation of bank statements.<br>Continuously identify process efficiencies and improve effectiveness. Adapt &amp; apply latest technology<br>available to automate finance &amp; accounting activities. Prepare and analyze financial data related to<br>operating expenses, capital expenses and Cash Flow. Analyze &amp; report budget variances to provide<br>Management with required information for action.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><strong>Job Requirements</strong></h2><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Must have Bachelor’s Degree in Accounting or (US Equivalent). Must have 3 years of accounting<br>experience including previous supervisory experience handling complex and large amount of financial<br>data accurately and efficiently. Experience in Financial statements preparation, Ad Hoc reporting,<br>Account analysis and reconciliations, monthly &amp; year-end closing activities and internal audit. Strong<br>understanding of AR, AP, General ledger, P&amp;L statements, balance sheet, Inventory Accounts,<br>Accounts reconciliation, Accrual and Planning and budgeting. Experience with Oracle ERP system and<br>J.D. Edwards. 20% International travel required. Applicant must have proof of legal authority to work<br>in the United States. 40 hours per week, M-F, 9:00am -5:00pm .</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><strong>How to Apply</strong></h2><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">To be considered, email your resume to: <a href=\"mailto:walbajes@cpapai.com\">walbajes@cpapai.com</a> at Precision Accounting International<br>located at 1035 US Highway 46, Suite # B-101, Clifton, NJ 07013. Must Reference #20221017.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">&nbsp;</p>', 'Senior Staff Accountant – Clifton, NJ', 'Prepare and process journal entries for miscellaneous accounts that may include AP, AR, GL, Inventory, investments, intercompany and other financial transactions.', 'Senior Staff Accountant – Clifton NJ', 'index, follow', 'Senior Staff Accountant – Clifton, NJ', 'place', '0', '{\"alt\":\"Senior Staff Accountant \\u2013 Clifton, NJ\",\"src\":\"Senior-Staff-Accountant-Clifton-NJ.webp\"}', NULL, '2023-09-12 09:28:24', '2024-03-11 01:57:27'),
