o catch up all the mail, but it takes longer.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Answering mailing usually takes almost 40 days but due to the current situation they delayed the days up to 60 days, so you have nothing to do with that just wait.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-left:!important;\"><strong>Reviewing tax returns, even for returns filed electronically:</strong></p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">If you need to fill a form with digital signature you can go directly to their official site to send the forms through the digital options.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">The IRS is taking all the responsibilities and considerations to keep its taxpayers and employees safe and healthy.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">In these challenging times, navigating tax complexities requires expertise more than ever. This is where <a href=\"https://cpapai.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span style=\"color:hsl(210, 75%, 60%);\"><strong><u>NJ Accountancy Experts</u></strong></span></a> come into the picture. They are well-equipped to provide personalized guidance and solutions, adapting to the rapidly changing tax landscape and ensuring that individuals and businesses in New Jersey stay compliant and informed.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Meanwhile, they are trying not to put off any of the services.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">In conclusion, we want to stress you to stay in touch with the online and live official site as we release all the processing activities, Stay tuned.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><strong>Resources:</strong></p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"https://www.irs.gov/newsroom/irs-operations-during-covid-19-mission-critical-functions-continue\"><strong>IRS.gov</strong></a></p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Internal_Revenue_Service\"><strong>Wikipedia</strong></a></p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">&nbsp;</p>', 'COVID-19 Affected The IRS Employees', 'COVID-19 has significantly impacted the employees of the Internal Revenue Service (IRS)', 'COVID-19 Affected The IRS', 'index, follow', 'COVID-19 Affected The IRS Employees', 'place', '0', '{\"alt\":\"COVID-19 Affected The IRS\",\"src\":\"How-COVID-19-Affected-The IRS-Employees.webp\"}', NULL, '2023-09-12 09:43:53', '2024-01-21 18:55:30'),
